run("
SELECT DISTINCT *
                ,ROUND(incm*NM3BO*internalSubo/spends,2) AS inm3PerCost
                ,ROUND((incm*NM3BO*internalSubo/spends-1)*spends,2) AS netBurn
FROM(
SELECT date_add('2022-01-02',cast(datediff(orderDate,'2022-01-02')/7 as int)*7) as week_start_date
        ,Campaign
        ,ROUND(AVG(increment),2) AS incm
        ,ROUND(AVG(panelSpends),0) AS spends
        ,ROUND(AVG(panelOrders),0) AS panelOrders
        ,ROUND(AVG(Suborders),0) AS internalSubo
        ,ROUND(AVG(ftuSubo)*100/AVG(shippedSubo),0) AS FTU_perct
        ,ROUND(AVG(appOrders)*100/AVG(Suborders),0) AS App_perct
        ,ROUND(AVG(NMIncAd),0) AS totalNM
        ,ROUND(AVG(NMIncAd)/AVG(Suborders)-9,2) AS NM3BO

FROM `temp.camp_roi`

WHERE DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 75

GROUP BY week_start_date
        ,Campaign
)

ORDER BY week_start_date DESC
",1000)

exportSQL(sql="
SELECT DISTINCT *
                ,ROUND(incm*NM3BO*internalSubo/spends,2) AS inm3PerCost
                ,ROUND((incm*NM3BO*internalSubo/spends-1)*spends,2) AS netBurn
FROM(
SELECT orderDate
        ,Campaign
        ,ROUND(AVG(increment),2) AS incm
        ,ROUND(AVG(panelSpends),0) AS spends
        ,ROUND(AVG(panelOrders),0) AS panelOrders
        ,ROUND(AVG(Suborders),0) AS internalSubo
        ,ROUND(AVG(ftuSubo)*100/AVG(shippedSubo),0) AS FTU_perct
        ,ROUND(AVG(appOrders)*100/AVG(Suborders),0) AS App_perct
        ,ROUND(AVG(NMIncAd),0) AS totalNM
        ,ROUND(AVG(NMIncAd)/AVG(Suborders)-9,2) AS NM3BO

FROM `temp.camp_roi`

WHERE DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 75

GROUP BY orderDate
        ,Campaign
) atb

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) AS date 
                        ,dayType 
        FROM `last75Days(saleDayMappingMaster)` 
        ) dt
ON atb.orderDate = dt.date

ORDER BY orderDate DESC
",path="/fb_Campaigns",format="csv",partitions=1,header="true")
